(1. Project Summary) Tj T*
(- Backend implements admin and user banking operations using Spring Boot.) Tj T*
(- Layered design with REST controllers, service logic, JDBC DAOs, and domain models.) Tj T*
(- MySQL-ready architecture with transaction logging and validation.) Tj T*
T*
(2. Architecture Overview) Tj T*
(- Controller Layer: AuthController, AdminController, UserController.) Tj T*
(- Service Layer: TransactionService, UserService, CreditRequestService, AuthenticationService.) Tj T*
(- DAO Layer: AccountDao, UserDao, TransactionDao, CreditRequestDao.) Tj T*
(- Model Layer: User, Account, Transaction, CreditRequest, Role, TransactionType.) Tj T*
(- Validation Layer: TransactionValidationChain and validator implementations.) Tj T*
T*
(3. Core Features Implemented) Tj T*
(- Admin login and user login.) Tj T*
(- User balance inquiry, transfer, transaction history, and credit request.) Tj T*
(- Admin user management, block/unblock, credit account, and audit transaction listing.) Tj T*
(- Transaction persistence and business validation before execution.) Tj T*
T*
