(- Singleton: DatabaseConnectionManager) Tj T*
(- Factory: UserFactory) Tj T*
(- Builder: TransactionBuilder) Tj T*
(- Command: Command interface, TransferCommand, CreditAccountCommand) Tj T*
(- DAO: AccountDao, UserDao, TransactionDao, CreditRequestDao) Tj T*
(- Chain of Responsibility: TransactionValidationChain plus validators) Tj T*
